title: Tezlyn Figaro: Democrats Are MISSING THE MARK, 'Your Social Media Presence Is NOT ENOUGH'

media:group.media:title: Tezlyn Figaro: Democrats Are MISSING THE MARK, 'Your Social Media Presence Is NOT ENOUGH'
media:group.media:description:
Host of "Straight Shot No Chaser" podcast Tezlyn Figaro weighs in on a new Marist-NPR-PBS Newshour poll which shows that Republicans are more enthusiastic about upcoming midterms than both Democrats and independents. #midterms #Democrats #Republicans
